Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:37.33,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9\fad(200,0)}从一起战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.33,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}那个人的背影里学到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.54,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}所以我不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.62,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我有必须要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.63,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}就算要毁灭地球也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.38,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就算要和他战斗也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.59,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9\fad(0,200)}所谓朋友就要保护朋友的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.39,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,0)}没错  这是那个人…地球的朋友教会我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.39,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9\fad(200,0)}所谓朋友就要保护朋友的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:17.62,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}什么情况!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.17,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.25,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}老师您在做什么呢\N快点去前线布阵吧\N将军已经出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.18,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.47,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.85,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}出击的顽侍突然爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.85,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(370,150)\frz10}什么  ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.35,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.36,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9\fad(200,0)}他们还有同伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.65,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}有间谍！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.45,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}母舰里混进了地球的间谍!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.82,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}出击中止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.45,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}立刻找出那几只老鼠来祭旗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.08,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}一只都不能放过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.87,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}喂  你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.87,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}那边是总督府
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.87,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(260,100)}怎么了\N怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:03.88,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(120,220)}你们去做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.88,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}有事告诉阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.13,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么!?  找到间谍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.89,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}你们…是那时的{\fscx200}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.89,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}难怪觉得你们可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.77,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}没想到竟是武士…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.77,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么你们会来到宇宙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.67,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}是右龙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.44,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}受死吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.20,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}你到底在打什么算盘？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.22,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8\fad(0,200)}生意？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.77,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}又要卖地球吗？ 打着这个旗号攻进这里的不也是你的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.53,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.85,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在开玩笑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.20,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}最后一击!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:40.14,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}胡说！ 攻进这个星球的你们会和我们一起攻打地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:34.27,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}攘夷志士？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.27,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}调查报告里没提到他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.11,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}立刻前去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.49,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an8}让他们全部化为宇宙的尘埃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.07,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}阁…阁下{\fscx200}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.07,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}后…后面!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.04,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.04,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.05,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an6}在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.33,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是…这是!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.33,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an5\pos(430,198)}阁…阁下{\fscx200}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.42,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}看来混进来的不只是老鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.18,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\an9}你算计我

